    "effect": "{{NAME}} can pick locks and pockets without even thinking about it. {{He}} can take one Larceny-based {{TOOLTIP:instant action,json.rules.instantAction}} {{TOOLTIP:reflexively,json.rules.reflexiveAction}} in a given turn.{{BR}}Additionally, {{his}} Larceny actions go unnoticed unless someone is trying specifically to catch {{him}}.",
    "source": {
